## Forms & client state

- Forms use **React Hook Form + Zod** via `@/components/ui/form.tsx`
  (shadcn pattern).
- Validation schemas are shared between client and server: prefer
  `@sous/types` (cross-app) over `apps/web/src/lib/validations/`
  (web-local); only put a schema in `src/lib/validations/` if it truly
  has no mobile counterpart.
- Client-side data fetching uses **TanStack Query v5** with the shared
  `QueryClient` from `src/components/shared/providers.tsx`. Prefer
  `useMutation` + server action over bespoke `fetch()` calls.
- Optimistic updates: use `onMutate` + `queryClient.setQueryData` with a
  rollback on error. See `ScheduleActions.tsx` for a reference.

